(39, 5, 7, 1, '<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:\n14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">1.<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">Se realiza\nel programa anual de auditorías internas con las fechas tentativas. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:\n14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">2.<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">Se envía\npor mail el programa anual de auditorías al Comité y la Gerencia.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:\n14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">3.<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">El día de\nla auditoría se revisan los 25 puntos de la norma teniendo como base el manual\nde calidad humana y responsabilidad social, utilizando la herramienta de\nauditoría interna 2014 proporcionada por Empresa Responsable.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:\n14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">4.<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">Se\nselecciona al azar empleados de la tienda para ser entrevistados.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:\n14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">5.<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">Se toman\nacciones a mejorar de las observaciones detectadas en conjunto con la\ncoordinadora y comité.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:\n14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">6.<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="ES" style="font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#7030A0;mso-ansi-language:ES">Se entrega\nun resumen de las observaciones y el resultado de la auditoria al Comité y a la\nGerencia para dar seguimiento.<o:p></o:p></span></p>   ', '', 0, 1, '2015-06-18 10:40:00', '2016-01-21 17:39:05'),
