al;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Otras\nprestaciones adicionales<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:\n10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\nmso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><b><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Existen diferentes formas para tasar el\nsalario:</span></b><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Salario fijado por unidad de tiempo: se paga\npor el tiempo que se dedica al trabajo, sin que importe la productividad;\nsimplemente se toma en cuenta un periodo: por hora, diario, semanal, quincenal,\nmensual, etcétera.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Salario por unidad de obra o "a\ndestajo": no importa el tiempo de producción sino las unidades producidas.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Salario por comisión: el porcentaje que se\npercibe sobre el producto de una venta o negocio.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Salario a precio alzado: se calcula por obra\nterminada pero el trabajador debe poner sus materiales y herramientas.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Salario de cualquier otra forma: algunos\nejemplos son salario por actuaciones (actores o músicos), salarios por\ntemporadas (deportistas), entre otros. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">De lo anterior es posible concluir que el\nsalario puede ser fijo o variable, depende de la forma cómo se obtenga.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Los trabajadores tienen derecho a disponer de\nsu salario de manera libre, lo cual implica que el patrón no puede limitarle\nesta facultad bajo ninguna circunstancia. El salario es irrenunciable,\ncualquier pacto en contra de este principio se considera inválido. Asimismo, no\nes posible que se apliquen multas bajo ningún concepto.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Es posible realizar deducciones en el salario\ndel trabajador, algunos casos son:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 15pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Pago\nde deudas contraídas con el patrón. El monto máximo permitido de este descuento\nes de 30%.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 15pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Pago\nde renta. No puede exceder de 25% del salario.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 15pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Pago\nde abonos para cubrir adeudos contraídos con el Fondo Nacional para la Vivienda\nde los Trabajadores.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 15pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Pago\nde las pensiones alimenticias cuando ha sido decretada por una autoridad\ncompetente.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 15pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">·<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Pago\nde cuotas sindicales.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:\n10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\nmso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Por otro lado, existe el concepto de salario\nmínimo, el cual se refiere a la cantidad menor que debe recibir en efectivo el\ntrabajador por los servicios prestados. Este salario es fijado por zona\ngeográfica y aplica para todos los trabajadores de dicha área sin importar la\nrama de actividad económica, profesión u oficio que desempeñe. Existen tres\náreas geográficas las cuales son A, B y C. En cada una de ellas la Comisión\nNacional de Salarios Mínimos se encarga de fijar el monto mínimo del salario.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><b><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Jornada de trabajo.</span></b><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Es el tiempo en el que el trabajador está a\ndisposición del patrón para prestar su trabajo.&nbsp; Puede ser diurna,\nnocturna, mixta o bien por horas.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Jornada diurna (ocho horas, comprendidas de\nlas 6:00 a las 20:00 horas).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Jornada nocturna (siete horas, comprendidas\nde las 20:00 a las 6:00 horas).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Jornada mixta (siete horas y media; comprende\nperiodos de tiempo de las jornadas diurna y nocturna, siempre que el periodo\nnocturno sea menor de tres horas y media, pues si comprende tres y media o más\nse establece como jornada nocturna).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Por horas (depende de lo que se haya pactado\ny su pago se obtiene de dividir ocho horas por el monto del salario mínimo\ngeneral vigente)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">La duración máxima de la jornada semanal es\nde 48 horas la diurna, 42 la nocturna y 45 la mixta.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">Durante la jornada continua de trabajo se\nconcederá al trabajador un descanso de media hora por lo menos. Cuando el\ntrabajador no pueda salir del lugar donde presta sus servicios durante las\nhoras de reposo o de comida, ese tiempo será registrado como tiempo efectivo de\nla jornada de trabajo. En el caso de madres trabajadoras, en los periodos de\nlactancia se les concede dos reposos extraordinarios por día, de media hora\ncada uno para alimentar a sus hijos.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">La jornada de trabajo se establece en el\nmomento de la contratación y podrá modificarse posteriormente. Es conveniente\nque dicha modificación conste en algún documento que firmen el trabajador y el\npatrón en el que acuerden la nueva jornada de trabajo, así como la fecha a\npartir de la cual se considerará el nuevo horario. Los trabajadores y el patrón\npodrán repartir las horas de trabajo con el objetivo de permitir a los primeros\nel reposo del sábado en la tarde o cualquier modalidad equivalente.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\nArial;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">La Ley Federal del Trabajo establece que las\nhoras extraordinarias se pagarán en proporción al salario que corresponda por\nhora de jornada ordinaria y menciona que toda retribución que reciba el\ntrabajador por su trabajo integra el salario. Por esto, el pago de horas\nextraordinarias también es un concepto que forma parte e integra la\nremuneración del trabajador. Se considera para el cálculo del pago de horas\nextraordinarias el salario diario base u ordinario que recibió el trabajador\ncomo parte de su trabajo.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 6pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 14pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; ba