mso-style-priority:99;\n	mso-style-qformat:yes;\n	mso-style-parent:"";\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n	font-size:10.0pt;\n	font-family:"Times","serif";\n	mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman";}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n\n<p style="margin-left:-70.9pt;text-align:justify"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">PROCEDIMIENTO DEL PROGRAMA <a name="proceso"></a></span></b></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">1.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">El Coordinador\nde Seguridad e Higiene del Corporativo diseñará el programa ???planta un árbol,\nplanta una vida??? que se implementará en las sucursales.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">2.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">El\ndepartamento de comunicación será el encargado de difundir este programa una\nvez que sea validado por el Comité de Calidad Humana, Responsabilidad Social y\nMejora Continua y autorizado por la Dirección General.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">3.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Una\nprimera etapa será realizar inventarios y monitoreo de las zonas que se puedan\nreforestar.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">4.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Los\ncoordinadores de Recursos Humanos detectarán zonas factibles de reforestación y\nrealizarán la gestión necesaria con los departamentos de ecología de cada\nciudad, solicitando el donativo de arboles que serán plantados.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">5.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Con el\nfin de tener un mayor impacto en la sensibilización del cuidado del medio\nambiente, se invitará a los hijos de los empleados para que participen junto\nco