margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:\nES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">1.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span></b><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">El área de Recursos Humanos del Corporativo determinará\nen qué puestos se puede contratar personal con discapacidad, adultos mayores y/o\nmujeres embarazadas.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:\nES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">2.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span></b><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">El área de Recursos Humanos reclutará, evaluará,\nseleccionará y contratará candidatos con discapacidad, adultos mayores y/o mujeres\nembarazadas para cubrir puestos específicos dentro de la organización.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:\nES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">3.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span></b><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Se realizará la campaña de <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal">No Discriminación</b>.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:\nES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">4.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span></b><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Al personal con discapacidad, adultos mayores y/o mujeres\nembarazadas se les deberá asignar un área donde desarrollen sus capacidades y\nhabilidades, salvaguardando siempre su integridad física y mental.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:\nES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">5.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span></b><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Fortalecer y ampliar la vinculación con las instituciones\nciviles ó de beneficencia pública, que atiendan ó cuenten con personas con discapacidad\ny puedan cubrir una vacante dentro de nuestra empresa. </span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:\nES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">6.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span></b><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Este programa se difundirá </span><span style="font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES-MX">mediante Banners ó Tablero de avisos ó revista\ninterna ó bolsas de empleo.</span><span style="font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"></span></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n   ', '', 0, 1, '2015-10-14 09:37:01', '2016-01-21 17:39:07'),
