han;\n	font-size:10.0pt;\n	font-family:"Times","serif";\n	mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman";}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n\n<p style="margin-left:-70.9pt;text-align:justify"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">PROCEDIMIENTO DEL PROGRAMA <a name="proceso"></a></span></b></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">1.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">El\nCoordinador de Seguridad e Higiene del Corporativo diseñará el programa de ZERO\naccidentes que se implementará en todas y cada una de las sucursales.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">2.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">El\ndepartamento de comunicación será el encargado de difundir este programa una\nvez que sea validado por el comité de Calidad Humana y Mejora y autorizado por\nla Dirección General.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">3.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Los\nCoordinadores de Recursos Humanos serán quienes difundan el programa e inviten\nal personal a participar en el mismo.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">4.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Se\nllevarán a cabo 2 semanas de la seguridad para todas las sucursales, donde\npodrán participar todos los empleados, proveedores y familias.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">5.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Mensualmente\nse medirá los accidentes registrados en las sucursales, sin embargo,\nTrimestralmente las sucursales que no tengan registrado ningún accidente ó\nincidente, serán acreedoras de un reconocimiento por parte del Director de\nRecursos Humanos.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">6.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Cada\nsucursal deberá realizar por lo menos una estrategia, que permita disminuir los\naccidentes o en efecto prevenirlos; con el fin de comunicarlos a todas las\nsucursales para la disminución de accidentes.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">7.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Se\ninvitará a proveedores a patrocinar lonas, letreros, etc.; que serán colocados\nen lugares estratégicos para apoyo a la comunidad para prevenir accidentes.</span></p>\n\n   ', '', 0, 1, '2015-10-15 13:27:49', '2016-01-21 17:39:07'),
