han;\n	font-size:10.0pt;\n	font-family:"Times","serif";}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n\n<p style="margin-left:-70.9pt;text-align:justify"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">PROCEDIMIENTO DEL PROGRAMA <a name="proceso"></a></span></b></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">1.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">El\nCoordinador de Seguridad e higiene<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>de\nCorporativo diseñará el programa para el cuidado y ahorro del agua.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">2.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">El\ndepartamento de comunicación será el encargado de difundir este programa una vez\nque sea validado por el Comité de Calidad Humana, Responsabilidad Social y\nMejora Continua y autorizado por la Dirección General.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">3.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Los\nCoordinadores de Recursos Humanos de las sucursales de Celaya, Guadalajara,\nMonterrey <span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span>y Distrito Federal serán\nquienes difundan de manera local el programa e inviten al personal a participar\nen el mismo.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:-34.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">4.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">El\npresente programa tiene contemplado llevar a cabo las siguientes actividades:</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:19.1pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:\nl0 level1 lfo2"><span style="font-family:Symbol;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:\nES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Principalmente realizar campañas de concientización sobre\nel uso y cuidado del agua, mediante charlas y/o entrega de material impreso. </span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:19.1pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:\nl0 level1 lfo2"><span style="font-family:Symbol;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:\nES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Se instalará planta de tratamiento de aguas residuales en\nla sucursal que cuente con áreas verdes y/o que su propio diseño estructural lo\npermita.</span></p>\n\n<p style="margin-left:19.1pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:\nl0 level1 lfo2"><span style="font-family:Symbol;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:\nES" lang="ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\nmso-ansi-language:ES" lang="ES">Instalar sistemas de ahorro de agua en las sucursales,\npor ejemplo: llaves de bajo flujo, mingitorios ecológicos, llaves ahorradoras,\ntanques de baja descarga, entre otros.</span></p>\n\n   ', '', 0, 1, '2015-10-16 17:59:13', '2016-01-21 17:39:07'),
